mmies-endorsement-a-hoax/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">Page Six</a> covered—and debunked—the hoax too. </p><p>And yet eleven months later a bunch of these fake sites are <em>still</em> there. A couple samples I grabbed from the web, yesterday:</p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9e61e95-c24c-4795-842b-922f456d0db2_1600x1263.jpeg" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/Cf3-9RAn59csKCHtr_ 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/g7DORbWSI-z9-lsavy2my- 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/FCIIPIPh--NzzGIvqhAL2Hn73g_ 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/EZg4PRR- 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux." alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux. 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/xfFaJww-jidCCOrMM1_YSC3J9YlEBCLeDnRTfh_bhYk=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd184NDgsY19saW1pdCxmX2F1dG8scV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkZmOWU2MWU5NS1jMjRjLTQ3OTUtODQyYi05MjJmNDU2ZDBkYjJfMTYwMHgxMjYzLmpwZWc= 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/EeO-wVC5EGbsarwtYyc4XMdPuBxn_ 1272w, https://reader.miniflux. 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"/></picture></a><figcaption>Exhibit 1</figcaption></figure><p></p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7be3afa9-d3ef-4fb2-bac6-3fddde228ead_1608x1333.jpeg" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/hoJIPFDltK0v7zwZMHa0C7v- 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/bhXnLodnUdmFarEDbU- 848w, https://reader.min